title: Queen + Adam Lambert - Tokyo, Japan - 17th August 2014 MultiCam
description:
Queen + Adam Lambert - Summer Sonic, Tokyo, Japan - 17th August 2014 MultiCam V2

H.264 1920 x 1080 HD, LPCM, 24000bitrate, 30fps.

Hi guys, this is my upgrade to the previously released share here: http://www.queenzone.com/forums/1395150/announce-queen-and-adam-lambert-tokyo-japan-17th-august-2014-multicam.aspx?anchor=1395150

This V2 has pro footage from the WoWoW broadcast featuring NIH, SCC, IWBTLY, CLTCL & WATC. Included with the pro footage is my own multicam from YouTube footage to complete this unedited concert. The audio is a lossless
rip of the audio shared here: http://www.queenzone.com/forums/1396210/queen-music-download-announce-q-and-al-2014-08-17-summer-sonic-2014-tokyo-japan-flac.aspx
The YT footage from me is a new edit in comparison to the older share too, with more stable footage and better shots added, so if you have the V1 I would recommend getting this too.

Thank you to all who contributed video and audio to this truly community project.
